This is a collection of a few of my old designs, and creates a full 500 point starting Mytho-Resistance warband for our [New Dominion](https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/illgottengames/new-dominion) project. I'll update here with some stats PDFs and links to the finished game once that's released, but in the meantime, print and paint away. Each of these need supports but I've included pre-supported versions as well.

For those of you who want to support what I do, please consider joining my [Ill Gotten Game Patreon](https://www.patreon.com/c/illgottengames). It really helps my little company to keep making stuff, and you'll get a bunch of our commercially released products as well. There are licensed seller options for those who want to sell 3d prints of our designs. Even the $1/month pledge level helps, and we have a humongous (and growing) collection of 300+ support free STLs to which you'll gain access to as soon as you pledge. Hope to see you there!
